[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m393[0m[39m:                            try [0m[1;39m{[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m394[0m[39m:                                [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Try to use the value as a formattable number[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m395[0m[39m:                                double d = [0m[1;35mDouble.parseDouble[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfv[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m396[0m[39m:                                thisStr = [0m[1;35mformatter.formatRawCellContents[0m[1;39m([0m[39md, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthis.formatIndex, this.formatString[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m397[0m[39m:                            [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mException e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m398[0m[39m:                                [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Formula is a String result not a Numeric one[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m399[0m[39m:                                [0m[1;35mLOG.atInfo[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.log[0m[1;39m([0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m400[0m[39m:                                        [0m[32m"Error formatting cell '[0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m' - will use [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mits raw value instead [0m[32m([0m[32mformat '[0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m'[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m,[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpoi/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/poifs/filesystem/DirectoryNode.jav[0m[1;92ma:80[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m96[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m80[0m[39m:        Iterator<Property> iter = [0m[1;35mproperty.getChildren[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m81[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m82[0m[39m:        while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35miter.hasNext[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m83[0m[39m:            Property child = [0m[1;35miter.next[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m84[0m[39m:            Entry childNode;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m85[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m86[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mchild.isDirectory[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m87[0m[39m:                DirectoryProperty childDir = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mDirectoryProperty[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m child;[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m88[0m[39m:                childNode = new [0m[1;35mDirectoryNode[0m[1;39m([0m[39mchildDir, _filesystem, this[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m89[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m90[0m[39m:                childNode = new [0m[1;35mDocumentNode[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mDocumentProperty[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m child, this[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m91[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m92[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35m_entries.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39mchildNode[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m93[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35m_byname.put[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mchildNode.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, childNode[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m94[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35m_byUCName.put[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mchildNode.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.toUpperCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLocale.ROOT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchildNode[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m95[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m96[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Overview of Root Causes  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. DirectoryNode unbounded recursion/iteration over child properties [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno depth [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mor entry limits[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. XSSFReader.getSheetsData iterates over all sheet relationships without cap.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. XSSFSheetXMLHandler loops over every XML token [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrows/cells[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with no row/cell [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcount limits.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Preservation of Critical Logic  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Existing parsing logic, block‐chain loop detection, and SAX event handling [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmust remain intact.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Timeouts should only occur on pathological inputs, not normal documents.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Default behavior for well‐formed, modestly sized files must be unchanged [0m[1;39m([0m[39mhigh[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mor disabled thresholds[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Introduce Configurable Guardrails  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Centralize configuration in a new `POIConfig` utility class [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor extend [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexisting POI settings[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      • maxDirectoryDepth [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdefault: [0m[1;36m64[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      • maxDirectoryEntries [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdefault: [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      • maxSheets [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdefault: [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      • maxRowsPerSheet [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdefault: [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      • maxCellsPerSheet [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdefault: [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      These defaults mirror realistic upper bounds and can be overridden via system[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mproperties or builder APIs.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Patch DirectoryNode Constructor [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mpoi/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/poifs/filesystem/DirectoryNode.java[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Add parameters or context fields for currentDepth and a shared entryCounter. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. On entry, increment depth; if depth > maxDirectoryDepth, throw [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Directory tree too deep"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Before processing each child, increment entryCounter; if entryCounter > [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmaxDirectoryEntries, throw [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Too many directory entries"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Pass incremented depth and shared counter into recursive `new [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mDirectoryNode[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Patch XSSFReader.getSheetsData [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mpoi-ooxml/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/xssf/eventusermodel/XSSFReader.java[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Before iteration, fetch maxSheets from config.  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Count relationships processed; if count exceeds maxSheets, throw [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mInvalidFormatException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Too many sheets"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Otherwise yield sheet InputStreams as before.  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Patch XSSFSheetXMLHandler [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mpoi-ooxml/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/xssf/eventusermodel/XSSFSheetXMLHandler.jav[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Introduce counters rowCount and cellCount in handler.  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. In `startElement`, when encountering `<row>`, increment rowCount; if > [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmaxRowsPerSheet, throw [0m[1;35mSAXException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Row count exceeds limit"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      Similarly, in `outputCell`, increment cellCount; if > maxCellsPerSheet, throw[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mSAXException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Cell count exceeds limit"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. These exceptions will abort parsing early, triggering a controlled failure [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrather than a hang.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Configuration and Defaults  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Expose setter methods on POIFSFileSystem and XSSFReader to override defaults [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mat runtime.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Support System.getProperty fallback [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `-Dpoi.[0m[33mmaxRowsPerSheet[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m5000000[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Document new config options in project README and Javadoc.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[39m. Justification and Side‐Effect Mitigation  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – By failing fast on clearly excessive structures, we prevent infinite loops and[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munbounded work.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – High default thresholds ensure ordinary large files are still supported.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Exposed configuration allows users to tune thresholds to their environment.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Exceptions thrown are specific [0m[1;39m([0m[39mIOException, InvalidFormatException, [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mSAXException[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and do not catch broader errors.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Existing unit tests on moderate‐sized POI documents remain unaffected; [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpathological fuzz inputs will exit promptly.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m9[0m[39m. Verification  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Add unit tests generating synthetic OLE2 directory trees beyond thresholds to [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mverify fast failure.  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Add synthetic XLSX packages with excessive sheets, rows, cells to ensure [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontrolled exceptions.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Confirm libFuzzer runs now complete without timeouts on known pathological [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minputs.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe Apache POI codebase was experiencing a libFuzzer timeout when exercising [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdocument tree traversal. A proposed patch added thread-local depth and entry [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcounters to `DirectoryNode.java` to limit recursion and prevent excessively deep or[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlarge directory trees. After applying the patch, the build failed with a flurry of [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompiler errors such as “illegal start of type” on import statements and “reached [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mend of file while parsing.”[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzer log reported a libFuzzer timeout, indicating one of the POI APIs [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mspecifically directory‐tree traversal in `DirectoryNode`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m was taking too long or [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecursing too deeply under fuzzed inputs.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No stack traces were shown before the timeout; the harness simply timed out.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `DirectoryNode.java`, the patch:  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Introduced two `ThreadLocal` counters [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`ENTRY_COUNTER`, `DEPTH_COUNTER`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • In the constructor [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor initialization block[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, incremented `DEPTH_COUNTER` and [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrew `IOException` if depth > `poi.maxDirectoryDepth` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdefault [0m[1;36m64[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Incremented `ENTRY_COUNTER` and threw if entries exceed [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`poi.maxDirectoryEntries` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdefault [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • After iterating children, decremented `DEPTH_COUNTER` and, if at the root [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`_parent == null`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, removed both `ThreadLocal`s.  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Added imports for `java.util.concurrent.atomic.*` and removed some existing [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimports [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. `java.util.List`, `java.util.Locale`, `java.util.Map`, [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`java.util.Set`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Adjusted whitespace and indentation.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Result  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The Java compiler reported errors beginning at line [0m[1;36m38[0m[39m: “illegal start of type” [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mon `import java.util.Spliterator;`. Similar errors appeared on all subsequent [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimport lines. Finally, “reached end of file while parsing” was raised.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Total of [0m[1;36m31[0m[39m errors, all pointing to mislocated or malformed import and class [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheader syntax.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mKey Observations  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. The errors occur at import statements that normally reside at the top of the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfile. Their being flagged as “illegal start of type” suggests they were shifted [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minto the class body or otherwise appear in an invalid context.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. The final “end of file while parsing” implies an unbalanced brace or missing [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclosing brace.  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. The patch diff shows the addition of `public final class DirectoryNode [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimplements DirectoryEntry [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m` appearing after some imports but before others, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicating the file’s structure got disrupted.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The top of `DirectoryNode.java`: confirm correct ordering of `package` [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeclaration, imports, and the class declaration.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Matching braces: ensure that the new constructor block and class body are [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mproperly opened and closed.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Verification of any removed imports [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. `List`, `Locale`, `Map`, `Set`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m—see if [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthey are still needed elsewhere in the file.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The exact insertion points of the patch hunks to reconstruct the original file [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maround lines [0m[1;36m23[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m44[0m[39m and around the child-iteration loop [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m77[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Surrounding context in `DirectoryNode` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmethods and fields[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to confirm that the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatch didn’t accidentally split or nest parts of the file incorrectly.[0m              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Restore the import and class‐declaration ordering:[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Revert the misplaced insertion of “public final class DirectoryNode implements[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDirectoryEntry [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m” from the import block. Ensure the file begins with:[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m `package org.apache.poi.poifs.filesystem;`[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m All `import` statements [0m[1;39m([0m[39mincluding the newly added ones[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in one contiguous [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mblock.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m A single `public class DirectoryNode [0m[33m...[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m` declaration immediately after [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe imports.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Add the needed imports for our ThreadLocal counters, directly below the last [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexisting import [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`import java.util.Spliterator;`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     import java.util.concurrent.atomic.AtomicLong;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     import java.util.concurrent.atomic.AtomicInteger;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Inside the `DirectoryNode` class, immediately after the existing field [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeclarations [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`_byname`, `_byUCName`, `_entries`, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, introduce two static [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThreadLocal counters:[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private static final ThreadLocal<AtomicLong> ENTRY_COUNTER =[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mThreadLocal.withInitial[0m[1;39m([0m[39mAtomicLong::new[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private static final ThreadLocal<AtomicInteger> DEPTH_COUNTER =[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mThreadLocal.withInitial[0m[1;39m([0m[39mAtomicInteger::new[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   This places them in class scope without disturbing existing fields or methods.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Update the constructor signature to declare that it throws `IOException` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mso our[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnew guards can throw checked exceptions[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;35mDirectoryNode[0m[1;39m([0m[39mDirectoryProperty property,[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   POIFSFileSystem filesystem,[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   DirectoryNode parent[0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Guard recursion depth at the very start of the constructor. Insert immediately [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mafter the opening brace `[0m[1;39m{[0m[39m`:[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     int depth = [0m[1;35mDEPTH_COUNTER.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.incrementAndGet[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     long maxDepth = [0m[1;35mLong.getLong[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"poi.maxDirectoryDepth"[0m[39m, 64L[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdepth > maxDepth[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mDEPTH_COUNTER.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.decrementAndGet[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Directory tree too deep: "[0m[39m + depth[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             + [0m[32m" exceeds max allowed "[0m[39m + maxDepth[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Wrap the entire original constructor body [0m[1;39m([0m[39mall of the code that sets [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`_filesystem`, builds `_path`, and iterates over children[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m inside a `try [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m … [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfinally [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m … [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` block, so the depth counter is always decremented:[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     try [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m existing logic: [0m[1;35msuper[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, set _filesystem, _path, and the while‐loop [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof children[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m finally [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Always decrement depth[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mDEPTH_COUNTER.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.decrementAndGet[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m If we’re back at the root, clear both ThreadLocals to avoid leaks[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mparent == null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mENTRY_COUNTER.remove[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mDEPTH_COUNTER.remove[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Inside the child‐iteration loop, before instantiating each child node, guard the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtotal entry count:[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     long totalEntries = [0m[1;35mENTRY_COUNTER.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.incrementAndGet[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     long maxEntries = [0m[1;35mLong.getLong[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"poi.maxDirectoryEntries"[0m[39m, 50000L[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtotalEntries > maxEntries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Too many directory entries in tree: "[0m[39m + [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtotalEntries[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             + [0m[32m" exceeds max allowed "[0m[39m + maxEntries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   This goes immediately before:[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     Property child = [0m[1;35miter.next[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[39m. Verify balanced braces:[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure the try block ends just before the `finally [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m … [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm there’s exactly one closing brace for the constructor.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm the class’s final `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` is present after all methods.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m9[0m[39m. Do **not** modify any harness, test code, or external libraries. This patch only[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtouches `DirectoryNode.java`. It preserves the original directory‐traversal logic, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlayering in two lightweight, thread‐safe guards that throw `IOException` when [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthresholds [0m[1;39m([0m[39mconfigurable via system properties[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are exceeded.[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m10[0m[39m. Rationale:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    - Correctly placing imports and the class declaration eliminates the “illegal [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstart of type” on imports and the “end of file while parsing” from mismatched [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbraces.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    - Declaring `throws IOException` on the constructor aligns with existing error [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatterns in the POI API when IO problems occur.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    - The try/finally ensures thread‐local counters are always cleaned up, even if [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma guard triggers an exception.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    - All existing functionality and APIs remain untouched for valid documents; [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39monly pathological deep/large trees [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe source of libFuzzer timeouts[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcurtailed.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe project’s continuous fuzzing harness reported a libFuzzer timeout when [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexercising the POI filesystem code. An attempted patch modified DirectoryNode.java [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto introduce thread-local counters for recursion depth and entry count, hoping to [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlimit or monitor traversal size. After applying the patch, the fuzzing run still [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mended with the same timeout error and no additional diagnostics.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The libFuzzer job stalled and ultimately timed out, indicating that some input or[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode path is leading to excessively long or unbounded processing.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The only observable fault was “ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout.” No stack trace or [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexception information was produced.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The harness simply invokes POI’s directory-tree handling and lets libFuzzer drive[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minputs; the harness has not been changed and is not believed to be the root cause. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mImportant Observations  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The timeout implies that the code under test spends too much time in one or more [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloops or recursive calls.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No Java-level exception or OOM was observed—only a lapse in expected termination [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtime.  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The error is reproducible both before and after the patch.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- File modified: [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpoi/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/poifs/filesystem/DirectoryNode.java  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Additions at the top of the class:  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Two ThreadLocal counters:  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – ENTRY_COUNTER [0m[1;39m([0m[39mAtomicLong[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to track the number of entries processed.  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – DEPTH_COUNTER [0m[1;39m([0m[39mAtomicInteger[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to track current recursion depth.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No code changes were shown that actually increment or check these counters, only [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtheir declarations.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After building with the patch and rerunning libFuzzer, the same “ERROR: [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibFuzzer: timeout” occurred.  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mReproduction Steps for Patch  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. In DirectoryNode.java, import `java.util.concurrent.atomic.AtomicLong` and [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`AtomicInteger`.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Declare:  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   private static final ThreadLocal<AtomicLong> ENTRY_COUNTER =  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35mThreadLocal.withInitial[0m[1;39m([0m[39mAtomicLong::new[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   private static final ThreadLocal<AtomicInteger> DEPTH_COUNTER =  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35mThreadLocal.withInitial[0m[1;39m([0m[39mAtomicInteger::new[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Recompile the project and rerun the existing fuzzing harness.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Observe that the run still times out with no change in behavior.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- DirectoryNode traversal methods: look at loops over entries and recursive descent[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto see if there are unbounded or poorly terminated paths.  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Any code that reads or loads POIFS streams or documents [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`POIFSBigBlockSize`, `POIFSDocument`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, since heavy I/O or large in-memory [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstructures could delay termination.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzing harness entry point: verify that the input-driving code does not [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minadvertently generate enormous in-memory structures that the library then tries to[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfully parse.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Methods in `DirectoryNode` that enumerate children [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35mgetEntries[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, [0m              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Interaction with any other thread-local or static state that might prevent [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcounters from being incremented or reset.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNo root cause or fix is provided here; this report is intended to document the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mobserved behavior, the attempted instrumentation patch, and the next code areas to [0m [2m                [0m
