[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m153[0m[39m:   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m154[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m155[0m[39m:   @Override[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m156[0m[39m:   public boolean [0m[1;35mhasEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString name[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m157[0m[39m:      if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mexcludes.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m158[0m[39m:         return false;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m159[0m[39m:      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m160[0m[39m:      return [0m[1;35mdirectory.hasEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m161[0m[39m:   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m162[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m163[0m[39m:   @Override[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m164[0m[39m:   public boolean [0m[1;35mhasEntryCaseInsensitive[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString name[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m165[0m[39m:      if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mexcludes.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m166[0m[39m:         return false;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m167[0m[39m:      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m168[0m[39m:      return [0m[1;35mdirectory.hasEntryCaseInsensitive[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m169[0m[39m:   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m170[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m171[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m172[0m[39m:   @Override[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m173[0m[39m:   public Entry [0m[1;35mgetEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString name[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws FileNotFoundException [0m[1;39m{[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m174[0m[39m:      if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mexcludes.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m175[0m[39m:         throw new [0m[1;35mFileNotFoundException[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m176[0m[39m:      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m177[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m178[0m[39m:      Entry entry = [0m[1;35mdirectory.getEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m179[0m[39m:      return [0m[1;35mwrapEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m180[0m[39m:   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m181[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m182[0m[39m:   @Override[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m183[0m[39m:   public Entry [0m[1;35mgetEntryCaseInsensitive[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString name[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mFileNotFoundException [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m184[0m[39m:      if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mexcludes.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m185[0m[39m:         throw new [0m[1;35mFileNotFoundException[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m186[0m[39m:      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m187[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m188[0m[39m:      Entry entry = [0m[1;35mdirectory.getEntryCaseInsensitive[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m189[0m[39m:      return [0m[1;35mwrapEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m190[0m[39m:   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m191[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m192[0m[39m:   private Entry [0m[1;35mwrapEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[39mEntry entry[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m193[0m[39m:      String name = [0m[1;35mentry.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m194[0m[39m:      if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mchildExcludes.containsKey[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m && entry instanceof DirectoryEntry[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m195[0m[39m:         return new [0m[1;35mFilteringDirectoryNode[0m[1;39m([0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m196[0m[39m:               [0m[1;39m([0m[39mDirectoryEntry[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mentry, [0m[1;35mchildExcludes.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m197[0m[39m:      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m198[0m[39m:      return entry;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m199[0m[39m:   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m200[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Overview and Root Cause  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The libFuzzer timeout stems from DirectoryNode’s unbounded traversal of POIFS [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdirectory trees: its constructor [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor entry‐loading method[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m recursively visits every[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchild property and populates large in‐memory lists and maps without any depth or [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentry‐count safeguards. Malicious or random inputs can thus generate extremely deep[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhierarchies or millions of entries, causing libFuzzer to stall until its timeout.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The previous patch merely declared thread‐local counters; it never incremented[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mor checked them, so no actual limiting occurred.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Core Strategy  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Introduce configurable, thread‐local recursion‐depth and total‐entry‐count [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlimits in DirectoryNode.  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Increment and check these counters at the start of each DirectoryNode [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvocation and before processing each child entry.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. On exceeding either limit, abort traversal of the current tree by throwing a [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchecked IOException. This short‐circuits the parse, returns control to the harness,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand prevents prolonged loops.  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Reset the thread‐local counters before parsing each new POIFS instance so [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat each fuzz input starts with fresh counters.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Detailed Steps  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. In DirectoryNode.java, define two new static constants near the ThreadLocal [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeclarations:  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        – MAX_RECURSION_DEPTH [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        – MAX_TOTAL_ENTRIES [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Augment the existing ThreadLocal fields as follows:  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        • Keep the thread‐local ENTRY_COUNTER and DEPTH_COUNTER declarations.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        • Add a static helper to reset them, for example:  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           public static void [0m[1;35mresetThreadLocals[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mENTRY_COUNTER.remove[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mDEPTH_COUNTER.remove[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. In the DirectoryNode constructor [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor the private method that iterates the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDirectoryProperty’s children[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        a. At the very start, call [0m[1;35mDEPTH_COUNTER.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.incrementAndGet[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           – If the returned depth exceeds MAX_RECURSION_DEPTH, immediately throw [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnew [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Maximum recursion depth exceeded: "[0m[39m + depth[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        b. Wrap the child‐processing loop in a try/finally block that decrements [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDEPTH_COUNTER in the finally clause.  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        c. Inside the loop, before handling each child, call [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mENTRY_COUNTER.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.incrementAndGet[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           – If the returned count exceeds MAX_TOTAL_ENTRIES, throw new [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Maximum entries processed exceeded: "[0m[39m + count[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        d. Proceed with the existing logic for creating DocumentNode or [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDirectoryNode children if limits are not exceeded.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. In POIFSFileSystem.java [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor the class/method that instantiates the root [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDirectoryNode for each input stream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        – Immediately before creating the root DirectoryNode, invoke [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mDirectoryNode.resetThreadLocals[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to clear any residual counts from previous runs. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. Ensure all thrown IOExceptions are allowed to bubble up to the harness; do [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnot catch them in DirectoryNode or related code. The harness will treat them as [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparse failures, not infinite loops.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Preservation of Existing Logic  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By throwing IOExceptions only when preset thresholds are exceeded, normal [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdocuments [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwith shallow hierarchies and modest numbers of entries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remain [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munaffected; all existing methods work as before.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The exception path is exercised only for aggressively deep or wide [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minputs—precisely those that are responsible for libFuzzer hang-ups.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Threshold Tuning and Side‐Effects  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Choose MAX_RECURSION_DEPTH and MAX_TOTAL_ENTRIES conservatively so valid [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreal‐world Excel/POIFS files don’t get rejected. For fuzzing, these limits should [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbe high enough to cover typical file sizes [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., depth ≤ [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m, entries ≤ [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbut low enough to cap pathological cases.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If legitimate files occasionally exceed the limits, users will see an [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException; documentation should note the new limits and how to adjust them via [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msystem properties or code constants.  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No global state beyond thread‐locals is introduced, so multi‐threaded usage in[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mproduction remains safe.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. References to Similar Patterns  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Other parts of POI already guard against unbounded resource use—for example, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min `POIFSBigBlockSize` there are checks on block counts. This patch follows the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msame “fail‐fast on excessive size” model.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The existing ThreadLocal declarations now become functional with [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mincrement/check/decrement, mirroring patterns seen in XML parser depth checks.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Verification  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add unit tests that build synthetic DirectoryProperty trees just over and just[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munder the limits, asserting that [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m files below thresholds parse successfully, and [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m those above thresholds throw IOException rapidly [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwithout significant CPU work[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Re-run the libFuzzer harness to confirm that timeouts disappear [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfuzz runs now[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mterminate quickly on pathological inputs[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run full regression suite to ensure no existing flood of IOExceptions on valid[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorpora.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis approach confines all changes to the core DirectoryNode and POIFSFileSystem [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclasses; it does not alter fuzz harness code, external libraries, or testing code, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthereby satisfying all patch constraints.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===[0m[33mIssue[0m[39m===[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue reported by the fuzzer was a timeout during corpus execution [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, indicating that POIFS parsing was either too deep or[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munbounded and never returned. In response, a patch was proposed that adds [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthread-local recursion-depth and entry-count limits to `DirectoryNode`, plus a [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mresetThreadLocals[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call before starting a new parse in `POIFSFileSystem`. After [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mapplying the patch, the Java compiler emitted a cascade of “illegal start of [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexpression” and “’;’ expected” errors throughout `DirectoryNode.java`, indicating a[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlikely syntax or brace-matching problem introduced by the patch.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A libFuzzer harness exercising Apache POI’s POIFS filesystem code reported a [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout, suggesting a pathological or infinite traversal in `DirectoryNode` when [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwalking a malicious or malformed OLE2 container.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No stack trace or Java exception was logged—only the fuzzer-level timeout—so [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwe know the traversal did not complete in the allotted time.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `DirectoryNode.java`:[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Imported `java.util.concurrent.atomic.AtomicLong` and `AtomicInteger`.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Declared two `ThreadLocal` counters: `ENTRY_COUNTER` for total entries seen,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand `DEPTH_COUNTER` for recursion depth.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Defined hard limits: `MAX_RECURSION_DEPTH = [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m` and `MAX_TOTAL_ENTRIES = [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m50000[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Added a public static `[0m[1;35mresetThreadLocals[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method to clear both [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthread-locals at the start of a parse.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Introduced a new constructor  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       `public [0m[1;35mDirectoryNode[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfinal POIFSFileSystem fs, final DirectoryProperty [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mproperty[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException`  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       that increments and checks `DEPTH_COUNTER` at entry, iterates children while[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchecking `ENTRY_COUNTER`, then decrements depth in a finally block.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `POIFSFileSystem.java`:[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • After reading the root `DirectoryProperty`, called [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mDirectoryNode.resetThreadLocals[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Instantiated the new `[0m[1;35mDirectoryNode[0m[1;39m([0m[39mthis, root[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` as `_root`.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Result  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Compilation failed in `DirectoryNode.java` at the new constructor declaration [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m103[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, with “illegal start of expression” and “’;’ expected” errors.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Subsequent method declarations throughout the class all triggered similar [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msyntax errors, suggesting that the new code introduced an unmatched brace or [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmisplaced token that shifted the compiler’s interpretation of the class body.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Observations & Next Steps  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The batch of parse-limit checks is conceptually in the right area [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtraversal [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min `DirectoryNode`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, but the compiler errors point to a structural issue in the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatched file.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - To get a holistic view, reviewers should inspect:[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • The brace structure in `DirectoryNode.java` around the newly added fields, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmethods, and constructor.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Whether the new constructor is inside the `DirectoryNode` class and not [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnested incorrectly inside another method or block.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Matching opening/closing braces for the preceding loop or class-level scope.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - It may also help to diff the patched file against a known-good version to [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlocate the stray or missing brace that is causing the cascade of syntax errors.[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m373[0m[39m:        return rval;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m374[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m375[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m376[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m377[0m[39m:     * create a new DocumentEntry[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m378[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m379[0m[39m:     * @param name the name of the new DocumentEntry[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m380[0m[39m:     * @param stream the InputStream from which to create the new[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Rethink where to inject recursion‐ and entry‐limit logic  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Rather than adding an entirely new public constructor [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhich led to misplaced [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35msuper[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` calls and unmatched braces[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, integrate the limit checks directly into [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe existing package-private traversal constructor. This keeps all recursive logic [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min one place, ensures the `[0m[1;35msuper[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call remains the first statement, and [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevents duplication or signature‐mismatch issues.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Add ThreadLocal counters and reset method  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   At the top of DirectoryNode.java [0m[1;39m([0m[39mjust after the existing imports[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, insert:[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Imports for `java.util.concurrent.atomic.AtomicLong` and `AtomicInteger`.  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Two `private static final ThreadLocal` variables: `ENTRY_COUNTER` and [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`DEPTH_COUNTER`.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Constants `MAX_RECURSION_DEPTH` and `MAX_TOTAL_ENTRIES`.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A public static `[0m[1;35mresetThreadLocals[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` that calls `[0m[1;35m.remove[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` on both [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthread-locals.  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   This block must be entirely within the class scope, before any constructors or [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmethods.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch the existing three-argument constructor  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Locate the original constructor signature [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m69[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;35mDirectoryNode[0m[1;39m([0m[39mDirectoryProperty property, POIFSFileSystem filesystem, [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDirectoryNode parent[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   and modify it as follows:[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Add `throws IOException` to its signature.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. At the very top of the constructor body, immediately after `[0m[1;35msuper[0m[1;39m([0m[39mproperty, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparent[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`, insert:  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      int depth = [0m[1;35mDEPTH_COUNTER.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.incrementAndGet[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdepth > MAX_RECURSION_DEPTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Maximum recursion depth exceeded: "[0m[39m + depth[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Wrap the remainder of the constructor in a `try [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m finally [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mDEPTH_COUNTER.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.decrementAndGet[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` block so that depth is decremented even [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif a child‐node creation fails.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Inside the existing `[0m[1;35mwhile[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35miter.hasNext[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` loop, before instantiating each [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchild node, add:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      long count = [0m[1;35mENTRY_COUNTER.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.incrementAndGet[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcount > MAX_TOTAL_ENTRIES[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Maximum entries processed exceeded: "[0m[39m + count[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      This ensures every entry [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdirectory or document[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m increments the total counter[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbefore recursion or node creation.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Remove the separate public constructor  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   The patch’s public `[0m[1;35mDirectoryNode[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPOIFSFileSystem, DirectoryProperty[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstructor and its mismatched braces should be deleted. All traversal now occurs [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min the single, unified constructor.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Reset counters before each top-level parse  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   In POIFSFileSystem.java, locate where the root `DirectoryNode` is constructed [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mimmediately after acquiring the `DirectoryProperty root`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. Insert a call to [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mDirectoryNode.resetThreadLocals[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` immediately before  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   _root = new [0m[1;35mDirectoryNode[0m[1;39m([0m[39mthis, root[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Verify brace matching and compiler requirements  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure the single constructor’s `[0m[1;35msuper[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` remains the first executable [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstatement.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm that every opening `[0m[1;39m{[0m[39m` has a matching `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mparticularly around the new[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`try/finally`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Make sure imports are at the top, static fields and methods are at class [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mscope, and no code is nested inside another method accidentally.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Preserve existing logic and APIs  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Do not alter any public APIs beyond adding `throws IOException` to the [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexisting constructor [0m[1;39m([0m[39mit’s package‐private, so no impact[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Keep all existing helper methods [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`getEntry`, `createDocumentInputStream`, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39metc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m untouched to maintain test and harness stability.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rely on the same recursion path built by the original constructor—only now it [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39menforces strict depth and entry limits.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[39m. Justification and side-effect mitigation  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Integrating limits into the existing constructor avoids duplicated code, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevents signature mismatches, and keeps `[0m[1;35msuper[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` correctly placed.  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Resetting thread-locals in POIFSFileSystem ensures limits start fresh per [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparse.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The `try/finally` guarantees `DEPTH_COUNTER` cannot leak a stale count on [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexception.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Limiting only in this core constructor covers all recursive traversal paths [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithout needing multiple overloads.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Any performance hit from atomic/thread-local operations is minimal and [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39macceptable given the need to prevent unbounded or maliciously deep OLE2 structures.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBy following this plan, the syntax errors vanish, recursion and entry limits are [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39menforced, and existing functionality—including all downstream methods and [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtests—remains intact.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         # Evaluation Report                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ## Summary                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - Initial issue: A libFuzzer job against the Apache POI codebase reported a timeout [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1m([0m“ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout”[1m)[0m with no further diagnostic output.                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - Patch attempt: A code change was proposed in `POIFSFileSystem.java` to adjust how [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         the root directory and data source are initialized. New references to               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         `DirectoryProperty.ROOT_NAME` and `[1;35mDirectoryNode.resetThreadLocals[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m` were added,   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         and the `_root` field was assigned before setting `_data`.                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - Result of the patch: The build failed during compilation of the `poi` module. Two [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         new compilation errors appeared in `POIFSFileSystem.java` [1m([0m“cannot find symbol” for [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         `ROOT_NAME` and `resetThreadLocals`[1m)[0m, preventing the patch from applying            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         successfully. The rest of the project compiled with warnings, but the errors in     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         these symbols stopped the overall build.                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ## Description                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m. Initial Issue                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - The fuzzing harness triggered a timeout in libFuzzer, indicating that no input [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         corpus exercised a crash or hang but instead the fuzzer reached its time limit.     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - No stack trace or exception was produced; the only message was “ERROR:         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         libFuzzer: timeout.”                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - The timeout suggests either an infinite loop, very slow path, or unresponsive  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         code under certain inputs in the POI codebase.                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m. Important Observations                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - The harness entry point invokes the POIFS [1m([0mPOI File System[1m)[0m routines, so       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         issues likely lie within the POIFS implementation or its initialization logic.      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - There is no direct indication of which method or class is causing the slowdown [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         or hang.                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - The timeout by itself does not imply a crash, but points to performance or     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         blocking behavior under fuzzing inputs.                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m. Patch Attempt                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Location:                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         `poi/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/poifs/filesystem/POIFSFileSystem.java`, around    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         line [1;36m257[0m.                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Original branch logic:                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              ```                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              FileBackedDataSource d = new [1;35mFileBackedDataSource[0m[1m([0msrcFile, readOnly[1m)[0m;          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              channel = [1;35md.getChannel[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m;                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              _data = d;                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              [1m}[0m else [1m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                _data = new [1;35mFileBackedDataSource[0m[1m([0mchannel, readOnly, closeChannelOnClose[1m)[0m;    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              [1m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              ```                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Proposed replacement [1m([0mcontextualized[1m)[0m:                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              ```                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              FileBackedDataSource d = new [1;35mFileBackedDataSource[0m[1m([0msrcFile, readOnly[1m)[0m;          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              channel = [1;35md.getChannel[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m;                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -    _data = d;                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -[1m}[0m else [1m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mgetProperty[0m[1m([0mDirectoryProperty.ROOT_NAME[1m)[0m;                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +    [1;35mDirectoryNode.resetThreadLocals[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m;                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +    _root = new [1;35mDirectoryNode[0m[1m([0mroot, this, null[1m)[0m;                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              _data = new [1;35mFileBackedDataSource[0m[1m([0mchannel, readOnly, closeChannelOnClose[1m)[0m;      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -[1m}[0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              ```                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Intention: Initialize the POIFS root node explicitly before assigning `_data`. [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m. Patch Result and Logs                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Compiler errors on the two added references:                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              * `DirectoryProperty.ROOT_NAME` could not be found in `DirectoryProperty`.     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         target.                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - No changes to other modules; the errors are localized to the changed file.     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         location.                                                                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m427[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Finally read the Small Stream FAT [0m[1;39m([0m[39mSBAT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m blocks[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m428[0m[39m:        BATBlock sfat;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m430[0m[39m:        _mini_store = new [0m[1;35mPOIFSMiniStore[0m[1;39m([0m[39mthis, [0m[1;35m_property_table.getRoot[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m431[0m[39m:        nextAt = [0m[1;35m_header.getSBATStart[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m432[0m[39m:        for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mint i = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < [0m[1;35m_header.getSBATCount[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m && nextAt != [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPOIFSConstants.END_OF_CHAIN; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m433[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mloopDetector.claim[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnextAt[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m434[0m[39m:            ByteBuffer fatData = [0m[1;35mgetBlockAt[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnextAt[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m435[0m[39m:            sfat = [0m[1;35mBATBlock.createBATBlock[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbigBlockSize, fatData[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m436[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35msfat.setOurBlockIndex[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnextAt[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m437[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35msbats.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39msfat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m438[0m[39m:            nextAt = [0m[1;35mgetNextBlock[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnextAt[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m439[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m440[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m441[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m442[0m[39m:    private void [0m[1;35mreadBAT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint batAt, ChainLoopDetector loopDetector[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws [0m     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m450[0m[39m:    private BATBlock [0m[1;35mcreateBAT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint offset, boolean isBAT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m451[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Create a new BATBlock[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m452[0m[39m:        BATBlock newBAT = [0m[1;35mBATBlock.createEmptyBATBlock[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbigBlockSize, !isBAT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m453[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mnewBAT.setOurBlockIndex[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m454[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Ensure there's a spot in the file for it[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m455[0m[39m:        ByteBuffer buffer = [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mByteBuffer.allocate[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mbigBlockSize.getBigBlockSize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m457[0m[39m:        long writeTo = [0m[1;35mMath.multiplyExact[0m[1;39m([0m[39m1L + offset, [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mbigBlockSize.getBigBlockSize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m458[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35m_data.write[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbuffer, writeTo[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m460[0m[39m:        return newBAT;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m89[0m[39m:               throw new [0m[1;35mIllegalArgumentException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Cannot create a [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mChainLoopDetector with negative size, but had: "[0m[39m + rawSize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m90[0m[39m:           [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m101[0m[39m:             [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m They're writing, and have had new blocks requested[0m              [2m                [0m
