[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m271[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m272[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Now process the various entries[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m273[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mreadCoreContents[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m274[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mIOException | RuntimeException e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m275[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Comes from Iterators etc.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m276[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m TODO Decide if we can handle these better whilst[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m277[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m  still sticking to the iterator contract[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m278[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcloseChannelOnError && channel != null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m279[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mchannel.close[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m280[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpoi/src/main/java/org/apache/poi/poifs/filesystem/DirectoryNode.jav[0m[1;92ma:69[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m96[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m69[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mDirectoryNode[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfinal DirectoryProperty property,[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m70[0m[39m:                  final POIFSFileSystem filesystem,[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m71[0m[39m:                  final DirectoryNode parent[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m72[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35msuper[0m[1;39m([0m[39mproperty, parent[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m73[0m[39m:        this._filesystem = filesystem;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m74[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m75[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mparent == null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m76[0m[39m:            _path = new [0m[1;35mPOIFSDocumentPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m77[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m78[0m[39m:            _path = new [0m[1;35mPOIFSDocumentPath[0m[1;39m([0m[39mparent._path, new String[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mproperty.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m}[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m79[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m80[0m[39m:        Iterator<Property> iter = [0m[1;35mproperty.getChildren[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m81[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m82[0m[39m:        while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35miter.hasNext[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m83[0m[39m:            Property child = [0m[1;35miter.next[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m84[0m[39m:            Entry childNode;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m85[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m86[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mchild.isDirectory[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m87[0m[39m:                DirectoryProperty childDir = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mDirectoryProperty[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m child;[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m88[0m[39m:                childNode = new [0m[1;35mDirectoryNode[0m[1;39m([0m[39mchildDir, _filesystem, this[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m89[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m90[0m[39m:                childNode = new [0m[1;35mDocumentNode[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mDocumentProperty[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m child, this[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m91[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m92[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35m_entries.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39mchildNode[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m93[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35m_byname.put[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mchildNode.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, childNode[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m94[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35m_byUCName.put[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mchildNode.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.toUpperCase[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLocale.ROOT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchildNode[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m95[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m96[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Initialization via [0m[1;35mPropertyTable.getRoot[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove references to non-existent constants and methods [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`DirectoryProperty.ROOT_NAME` and `[0m[1;35mDirectoryNode.resetThreadLocals[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - After the property table is read [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi.e., after `[0m[1;35mreadCoreContents[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, call:[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       _root = new [0m[1;35mDirectoryNode[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_property_table.getRoot[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, this, null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This uses the existing `[0m[1;35mPropertyTable.getRoot[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` API, which returns a [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`RootProperty` instance [0m[1;39m([0m[39ma subtype of `DirectoryProperty`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Place this assignment immediately after `[0m[1;35mreadCoreContents[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in all [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstructors, ensuring `_root` is correctly initialized before any subsequent [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlookups.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Correct Data Source Branch Logic:[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the File-backed constructor [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe branch taking a `File srcFile`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, restore [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe original `_data = d;` assignment.[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Do not prematurely assign `_data` to a channel-only data source before setting[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`_root`. Instead:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     FileBackedDataSource d = new [0m[1;35mFileBackedDataSource[0m[1;39m([0m[39msrcFile, readOnly[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     channel = [0m[1;35md.getChannel[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     _data = d;                    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m restore this assignment[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Then, after `_data` is set and before returning from the constructor, call [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mreadCoreContents[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and initialize `_root`.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Unify Initialization Across Constructors:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - For the constructor taking a `ReadableByteChannel`, ensure the same sequence:[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Assign `_data` via the channel-backed `FileBackedDataSource`.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Call `[0m[1;35mreadCoreContents[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - Initialize `_root` from `[0m[1;35m_property_table.getRoot[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Preserve Existing Behavior and Avoid Harness Changes:[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Do not modify any fuzzer harness or test code.[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Do not introduce new thread-local clear methods; rely on fresh `DirectoryNode`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstruction to avoid stale state.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure existing API contract for directory traversal and lookups is unbroken.[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Steps to Implement:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m In `POIFSFileSystem.java`, locate every constructor entry [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mPOIFSFileSystem[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFile, boolean[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, `[0m[1;35mPOIFSFileSystem[0m[1;39m([0m[39mReadableByteChannel, boolean[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Immediately after calling `[0m[1;35mreadCoreContents[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, add:[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      _root = new [0m[1;35mDirectoryNode[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35m_property_table.getRoot[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, this, null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m In the File-backed branch [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround original patch at line [0m[1;36m257[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, revert to:[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      FileBackedDataSource d = new [0m[1;35mFileBackedDataSource[0m[1;39m([0m[39msrcFile, readOnly[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      channel = [0m[1;35md.getChannel[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      _data = d;[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Remove all code referring to `DirectoryProperty.ROOT_NAME` and [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mDirectoryNode.resetThreadLocals[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Compile and run existing tests to verify no regressions.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Justification:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `[0m[1;35mPropertyTable.getRoot[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` is the documented way to fetch the root property; it[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mavoids reliance on a missing constant.[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `DirectoryNode` constructors already rebuild all children fresh, so no manual [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthread-local reset is needed.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Restoring `_data = d;` ensures the correct backing data source is used, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreventing potential hangs from misconfigured sources.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This approach preserves existing initialization order, simply inserting a [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorrect root initialization step after the property table has been built.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Side Effects and Mitigation:[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Minor performance overhead from explicitly building the root directory on [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mload; negligible compared to file parsing.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No change to public APIs; consumers of `POIFSFileSystem` see the same `_root` [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvia `[0m[1;35mgetRoot[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` or iteration methods.[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Verify that no other code paths set `_root` redundantly; if they do, ensure [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39midempotence by checking for null before assignment.[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBy following these steps, the missing-symbol compilation errors are resolved, and [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe POIFS root node is correctly initialized after reading the property table, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39meliminating potential hangs due to uninitialized directory state under fuzzing. [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
